subject: meta-fii/meta-kudo: Modify virtual sensor config
commitMessage:
meta-fii/meta-kudo: Modify virtual sensor config

Add CPU detect to support 1p/2p virtual sensor json
configuration
Add new thermal sensors
Add virtual sensor json selection support based on
NBM chipset version
